article_title: NU coach Yori suffers 'scary' collapse during Husker win
article_text:
Previous Next NU coach Yori suffers 'scary' collapse during Husker win Nebraska coach Connie Yori watches the Huskers play the Hoosiers in the first half at Pinnacle Bank Arena Sunday in Lincoln. Yori later collapsed.
